      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah, of course being mutable would only matter if we were using a const function (eg, setHasSideEffects) to do this, but we\u0027re accessing the field directly. We could add such a thing, to make this look less suspicious, but we still have the bigger issue of unsafe access to symbols.",
